      "paper_id": "A17",
      "doi": null,
      "title": "Low-density Fe40Mn19Ni15Al15Si10C1 high entropy steel processed by mechanical alloying and spark plasma sintering: Phase evolution, microstructure and mechanical properties",
      "authors": [
        "Harsh Jain",
        "Yagnesh Shadangi",
        "Dibyendu Chakravarty",
        "Kausik Chattopadhyay",
        "Ashutosh Kumar Dubey",
        "N.K. Mukhopadhyay"
      ],
      "publication_year": null,
      "journal": null,
      "keywords": [
        "High entropy steel",
        "Mechanical milling and spark plasma sintering",
        "Phase evolution and microstructure",
        "Thermal stability",
        "Mechanical properties",
        "Strengthening mechanisms"
      ],
      "research_type": "mixed",
      "paper_scope": "研究机械合金化结合放电等离子烧结制备的非等原子比Fe40Mn19Ni15Al15Si10C1低密度高熵钢的相演化、微观结构、热稳定性及力学性能，结合热力学参数、CALPHAD模拟和强化机理解释性能起源，为兼具高强度与高温稳定性的高熵钢设计提供实验依据"
    }
  ],
